You know its funny at 34 when my chanter was growing up I was working to get a BCR to drop.  I never got one, ended up with Crystalline Robes that lasted me into my 50s when I started my epic and camped the SMR.  I used the SMR until I got a Vah Shir Skin Robe to drop.<br>
<br>
I would replace the Robe, Head, the right ear, the PBB.<br>
<br>
Ok I would get a new Range slot as well.  I would do so in ways that are going to last for a long time.<br>
<br>
Robe - Go to an SMR, you will need for your epic anyway.<br>
Right Ear - Get a Earring of the Solstice<br>
PBB - Get a Bracer of Comphrension<br>
Head - I have had a lot of trouble with this slot till I got a HoT drop for it Runed Cowl maybe?<br>
Range Slot - I am terrible at Range Slots, mine is the Velks drop.  Hive Fiend's Brain maybe.<br>
<br>
None of this stuff that I have mentioned is cheap.  On my server (Vazelle), I think this stuff would equate to about 25K.  If you still have money then....<br>
<br>
Other items to ponder:<br>
Velketor's Spellbook<br>
Ornate Runed Shield<br>
Crashing Wave Earing<br>
Iron Amulet of Unseen Horrors<br>
Robe of Haunted Dreams<br>
<br>
